data.description: Price Reduced, Reduced! Location, Location sought after neighborhood of Sunset Harbour.  Corner house with ample space for a boat or RV Look no further than this beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-baths home with a 1 car garage and tons of potential.  This home boasts a lovely backyard perfect for relaxing and entertaining.  Inside a spacious living room, comfortable bedrooms, remodeled kitchen and one bathroom and shutters.  Ample natural light throughout. This home has endless possibilities to become your dream home.  Near A+ schools, great shopping, dining and with many community extras like, pool, jacuzzi, clubhouse, basketball, tennis and racquetball courts just to name a few.
